'''莫貴茨·馬西西'''（{{lang-en|Mokgweetsi Masisi}}，{{bd|1961年|7月21日||}}），男，[[波札那|波札那]]政治人物、第五任總統。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.gov.bw/en/News/Masisi-is-the-Vice-President-of-the-Republic/|title=PROFILE OF HIS HONOUR MOKGWEETSI ERIC KEABETSWE MASISI, VICE PRESIDENT OF THE REPUBLIC OF BOTSWANA|work=波扎那政府|access-date=2017-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141129023438/http://www.gov.bw/en/News/Masisi-is-the-Vice-President-of-the-Republic/|archive-date=2014-11-29|url-status=dead}}</ref>

== 生平 ==
2009年，馬西西首次当选议会议员。2011年至2014年，馬西西出任总统事务和公共管理部长。2014年起擔任教育部长。2018年起擔任波札那總統<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://mg.co.za/article/2018-04-03-who-is-botswanas-new-president-mokgweetsi-masisi/|title=Who is Botswana’s new President Mokgweetsi Masisi?|first=INK Centre for Investigative Journalism, Botswana|last=Guardian|website=The M&G Online|accessdate=2019-05-14}}</ref><ref name="DW">{{Cite web|url=https://www.dw.com/en/botswana-mokgweetsi-masisi-takes-over-presidency-amid-opposition-resurgence/a-43206610|title=Botswana: Mokgweetsi Masisi takes over presidency amid opposition resurgence |website=[[Deutsche_Welle|Deutsche Welle]] |date=2018-03-31|accessdate=2019-05-14}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.france24.com/en/20180401-botswana-inaugurates-new-president-masisi-smooth-handover|title=Botswana inaugurates new president Masisi in smooth handover|date=2018-04-01|website=France 24|accessdate=2019-05-14}}</ref>。

